#. Tag: para
#: association_mapping.xml:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <emphasis>bidirectional one-to-one association on a join table</emphasis> "
"is extremely unusual, but possible."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>基于连接表的双向一对一关联</emphasis>极为罕见，但也是可行的。"

#. Tag: programlisting
